== 对外投资 ==
据报道截止2014年底，中投所管理的资产总额7467.3亿美元；大约60%资产投资于[[美国|美国]]，其余投资于[[欧洲|欧洲]]、其他亚洲国家和[[加拿大|加拿大]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-09/china-sovereign-fund-has-about-60-of-assets-invested-in-u-s-jin-says.html |title=China’s CIC Has About 60% of Assets in U.S. |accessdate=2011-12-11 |archive-date=2014-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140804021119/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-09/china-sovereign-fund-has-about-60-of-assets-invested-in-u-s-jin-says.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

